title: DDFP 449:  Eagles-Browns Trade & All-time NFL Draft of 2016 Picks 26-32
itunes:title: DDFP 449:  Eagles-Browns Trade & All-time NFL Draft of 2016 Picks 26-32
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank and NFL.com Fantasy Writer/Editor Alex Gelhar as they discuss the Eagles trading for the No. 2 pick in the 2016 NFL Draft and the Panthers decision to rescind the franchise tag from Josh Norman. Then, the guys break down picks 26-32 of the All-Time Draft of 2016.
